e south of France , I have a passion for\nnavigation in the Mediterranean, There are so many beautiful stopovers and anchorages that I love\nto attend. It is with the same passion that I take charge of a ship with self-reliance, a collaborative\nspirit, and a constant focus on my passengers’ well-being."},{"name":"Callan McCulley","avatar":"/media/media::image::c::17338971224::vessel::1228a120-68fa-11ef-a710-5b623bea5cd1::assets::c0d8fd00-5c15-11f0-83a0-814f59ba7179/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"I am an enthusiastic and quick-learning South African with a passion for the yachting industry, seeking to further develop my expertise. Over the past two seasons, I have gained valuable experience in various roles, including deck chef, crew cook, steward, and deckhand. I am particularly interested in pursuing a position as a chef/cook or deckhand.\n\nMy background combines creativity and practicality, enabling me to thrive in high-pressure, fast-paced environments that often require long hours. I spent nearly two years working in a professional kitchen in Germany, where I catered to events with up to 350 guests. This experience honed my skills in teamwork, reliability, efficiency,\nand responsibility.I excel in managing social interactions with guests, supported by a positive attitude and strong problem-solving capabilities.\nI"},{"name":"Thays Monteiro","avatar":"/media/media::image::c::17338971224::vessel::1228a120-68fa-11ef-a710-5b623bea5cd1::assets::547e8a70-615c-11f0-9796-218f8660e3e0/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"With over 2,000 nautical miles logged in the Caribbean and along the Brazilian coast, Thays is a skilled and adaptable stewardess with experience on both private and charter yachts. She combines top-tier guest service with hands-on support in sailing, provisioning, and interior care. Fluent in Portuguese, English, and Spanish, Thays is known for her warm demeanor, creativity, and dedication to delivering an exceptional onboard experience."